          "settings": {
            "heading": "Handcrafted Block Printing Meets Luxury Interior Design"
          }
        },
        "text_r4bhaE": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Remaining true to her signature aesthetic, Molly Mahon brings each design to life using traditional block printing techniques. Every tulip begins as a hand carved block, celebrating the artistry and craftsmanship behind her roots in luxury fabric and wallpaper design.</p><p>The colour palette introduces a softer, more atmospheric direction. Drawing on muddied Dutch tones and the romance of antique herbaria, the collection features deep blacks lifted with emerald greens, alongside warm golds and muted rose hues. These combinations create a layered, tonal richness - ideal for interior designers and homeowners looking to add depth, texture, and warmth to a space.</p>",
            "code": ""
          }
        }
      },
