    "image_with_text_AwtNFg": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_iJmJpY": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Styling Botanica, The English Cottage"
          }
        },
        "text_qGWCe4": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Shot in Molly Mahon’s own workshop, set within the picturesque Sussex countryside, the <em>Botanica</em> collection truly comes into its own. Surrounded by a working farm landscape, the setting reflects the spirit of the designs - rooted in nature, craft, and quiet rural beauty.</p><p>Each print sits effortlessly within the workshop’s rustic interior, complementing aged woods and natural textures. The result is a relaxed yet elevated take on the English country cottage aesthetic, where pattern and colour bring a warm, considered charm in Molly’s signature style.</p><p>We loved seeing the tones come to life across the space. Black/Emerald introduces drama and depth to a bedroom, creating a cocooning feel, while Olive/Gold adds warmth and character in the kitchen. Meanwhile, the softer Rose palette brings a light, elegant touch to the living room.</p>",
            "code": ""
          }
        }
      },
